item.title: Burke Azbill returns to the VMware Communities Roundtable
item.description: Hello all, it looks like we have Burke Azbill participating in this week’s VMware Communities Roundtable (Episode #130) Podcast by @jtroyer. Be sure to stop by! The session will be discussing vCloud Connector and other delights, including that new Plug-in that allows vCenter Orchestrator to work with vCloud Director!
